<div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl shadow-lg p-10 text-center space-y-4">
    <section class="py-20 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-900">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Implementation (My Side of the Project)</h2>
        
        <div class="relative border-l-4 border-blue-500 dark:border-blue-400">

        <!-- Item 1 -->
        <div class="mb-10 ml-6">
            <div class="absolute -left-3 flex items-center justify-center w-6 h-6 bg-blue-500 rounded-full ring-8 ring-blue-100 dark:ring-gray-900 dark:bg-blue-400"></div>
            <time class="mb-1 text-sm font-medium text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">11/9</time>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Floor and Passenger Class</h3>
            <ul class="mt-2 list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
            <li>Basic variables and logic regarding the addition of passengers to a floor queue</li>
            <li>Basic getters and setters for necessary variables</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Item 2 -->
        <div class="mb-10 ml-6">
            <div class="absolute -left-3 flex items-center justify-center w-6 h-6 bg-blue-500 rounded-full ring-8 ring-blue-100 dark:ring-gray-900 dark:bg-blue-400"></div>
            <time class="mb-1 text-sm font-medium text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">11/15</time>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Implemented a Basic GUI</h3>
            <ul class="mt-2 list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
            <li>Basic floor and elevator pictures in window</li>
            <li>Added Run, Enable/Disable logging</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Thanksgiving Break -->
        <div class="mb-10 ml-6">
            <div class="absolute -left-3 flex items-center justify-center w-6 h-6 bg-yellow-500 rounded-full ring-8 ring-yellow-100 dark:ring-gray-900 dark:bg-yellow-400"></div>
            <time class="mb-1 text-sm font-medium text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Week of 11/24</time>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Week Off for Thanksgiving</h3>
        </div>

        <!-- Item 3 -->
        <div class="mb-10 ml-6">
            <div class="absolute -left-3 flex items-center justify-center w-6 h-6 bg-blue-500 rounded-full ring-8 ring-blue-100 dark:ring-gray-900 dark:bg-blue-400"></div>
            <time class="mb-1 text-sm font-medium text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">12/2</time>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Basic FSM in Building</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
            Load, Unload, Stop, MV1Flr, MV2Flr, OPENDR, CLSRDR
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Item 4 -->
        <div class="mb-10 ml-6">
            <div class="absolute -left-3 flex items-center justify-center w-6 h-6 bg-blue-500 rounded-full ring-8 ring-blue-100 dark:ring-gray-900 dark:bg-blue-400"></div>
            <time class="mb-1 text-sm font-medium text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">12/6</time>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Skip and Give Up Logging Functionality</h3>
        </div>

        <!-- Item 5 -->
        <div class="mb-10 ml-6">
            <div class="absolute -left-3 flex items-center justify-center w-6 h-6 bg-green-500 rounded-full ring-8 ring-green-100 dark:ring-gray-900 dark:bg-green-400"></div>
            <time class="mb-1 text-sm font-medium text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">12/6</time>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Successfully Passed All JUnit Tests</h3>
        </div>

        <!-- Item 6 -->
            <div class="ml-6">
                <div class="absolute -left-3 flex items-center justify-center w-6 h-6 bg-blue-500 rounded-full ring-8 ring-blue-100 dark:ring-gray-900 dark:bg-blue-400"></div>
                <time class="mb-1 text-sm font-medium text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">12/12</time>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Updates To GUI</h3>
                <p class="mt-2 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
                Show number of passengers waiting in each group
                </p>
            </div>

            </div>
        </div>
        </section>
    </div>
    <section id="analysis" class="py-20 flex justify-center bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-900">
  <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl shadow-lg p-10 text-center space-y-6 max-w-4xl w-full">
    
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Analysis</h2>
    
    <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
      We found that <span class="font-semibold">Elevator 3</span> was the best configuration,
      achieving the <span class="font-semibold">lowest average wait time</span> and the 
      <span class="font-semibold">fewest passengers who gave up</span>.
    </p>

    <img src="/personal_Portfolio/elevator-sim.png" alt="Elevator Simulation Graph"
         class="rounded-lg shadow-md mx-auto">

    <a href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/1oIVnv9lOpKloKNAs_hVz6N-fxVjgfn6SYrHmJ3q8Hzo/edit?tab=t.0" 
       class="inline-block bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-purple-600 text-white font-semibold py-3 px-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl hover:opacity-90 transition" target = "_blank">
       View Full Analysis
    </a>

  </div>
</section>
<section id="conclusion" class="py-20 flex justify-center bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-900">
  <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl shadow-lg p-10 text-center space-y-6 max-w-4xl w-full">

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Summary of Learning</h2>

    <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
      Throughout the project, my partner and I encountered several tough challenges and at times felt like we would never see the end of the tunnel. 
      While the project may not have seemed complex at a glance, I learned how much effort it takes to synchronize every detail between multiple people 
      working on the same assignment. It took us a few days to figure out how to work together effectively, but once we did, we were able to complete 
      tasks on time and break the project down into small, manageable pieces to keep everything on schedule. 
      Overall, it was a great experience that introduced me to the workflow and process of larger collaborative projects.
    </p>

  </div>
</section>

  <!-- github button -->
<a href="https://github.com/lance-kluge/ElevatorSim" target="_blank"
   class="fixed bottom-8 right-8 px-8 py-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-purple-600 
          text-white text-lg font-bold rounded-full shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl 
          transition-all z-50">
  View on GitHub
</a>

</section>




    <!-- Footer Component -->
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>
